                ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 16 Jul 2016 22:30:00 +0800";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"http://www.zhihu.com/question/20209705/answer/40278241";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"方凡浅";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:12;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Party at Shoreline Amphitheatre";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:101:"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/21543781?utm_campaign=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss&utm_content=title";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11911:"<img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/be3b83e51da2f776809e0fa5e909e0c6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1440" data-rawheight="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1440" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/be3b83e51da2f776809e0fa5e909e0c6_r.jpg">今年 5 月份，我和朋友去 Mountain View 参加了 Google I/O 2016。今年的 I/O 大会是在室外举行的，Google 将总部旁边的 Shoreline Amphitheatre，一个巨大的露天剧场装扮成了今年的 I/O 会场。<p>虽然是是一个技术盛会，但是我却一点都不觉得枯燥，持续三天的大会就像是一场盛大华丽的 party，让我情绪高涨，好奇心爆棚。下面就带大家逛一逛这场在 Shoreline Amphitheatre 的 party。<br></p><p>▼ 等待 Keynote<br></p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2b8585c3586db54942dbf504218c0846_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="3024" data-rawheight="3024" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="3024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/2b8585c3586db54942dbf504218c0846_r.jpg"><p>大会前一天签到的时候发了一件 T 恤，并且现场拍照打印了 badge。</p><p>▼ <b>GEO</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c63f6aea8e7c67f28922291dc58fd91b_b.png" data-rawwidth="1031" data-rawheight="774" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1031" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c63f6aea8e7c67f28922291dc58fd91b_r.png">▼ <b>桌上足球</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/e00cb6b85dbaefc9d0d4f5a4a39ce491_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/e00cb6b85dbaefc9d0d4f5a4a39ce491_r.png">现场有好几个桌上足球，都有自动计分的功能，计分系统是使用 Firebase 搭建的。Firebase 今年真是火得一塌糊涂，新出的功能也确实不负众望，可以真正做到让开发 App 的人不用操心后台。</p><p><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//firebase.google.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Firebase 官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br></p><p>▼ <b>Android Experiments</b><br></p><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/d7462f473bc97987c25c281faa4a2807_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/d7462f473bc97987c25c281faa4a2807_r.png"><p><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.androidexperiments.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Android experiments 官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a> 的介绍：<br></p><blockquote><p>Android was created as an open and flexible platform, giving people more ways to come together to imagine and create. Developers everywhere have used the unique capabilities of the platform to push the limits of what’s possible on phones, tablets, watches and beyond.</p><p>We’re working to document creative experiments like these and make them open source so anyone can see how they are made, or get inspired to create their own. Our hope is to encourage more developers to challenge how we interact with the devices we use every day.</p><p>Each experiment is submitted by the creator, and all kinds are welcome—no matter your skill level, the framework it uses or the device it runs on. If you’ve created something amazing on Android you’d like to share, please <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.androidexperiments.com/submit" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">submit your own experiment.<i class="icon-external"></i></a></p></blockquote><p>▼ <b>Android Auto</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/408eb23f48630e3141787e334b48fc2e_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/408eb23f48630e3141787e334b48fc2e_r.png"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.android.com/auto/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Android Auto 官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br></p><p>▼ <b>Nest 展位</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0a7b039becd0ed9381b946b543c5b1ea_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0a7b039becd0ed9381b946b543c5b1ea_r.png">▼ <b>Project Bloks</b><br></p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1eb2ae9a2d5a2d86fe99e5f2db9484d9_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/1eb2ae9a2d5a2d86fe99e5f2db9484d9_r.png"><p><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//projectbloks.withgoogle.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Project Bloks 官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br></p><blockquote>Project Bloks is a research project. Our aim is to create an open hardware platform to help developers, designers, and researchers build the next generation of tangible programming experiences for kids.<br></blockquote><p>▼ <b>Project Tango</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/833a4ddbf6a6342897e48ae9704b1203_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/833a4ddbf6a6342897e48ae9704b1203_r.png"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//get.google.com/tango/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Project Tango 官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br></p><p>前段时间联想和 Google 合作推出了第一款支持 tango 的手机 Phab2 Pro。</p><p>▼ <b>Material Design Reviews</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/bcc0cbe6666fa506e67f4dbb5d7b3ee3_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/bcc0cbe6666fa506e67f4dbb5d7b3ee3_r.png">Material design 的官方网站上个月刚刚换了新的域名：<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//material.google.com/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="visible">material.google.com/</span><span class="invisible"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a></p><p>▼ <b>Gbike</b><br></p><br><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/0797f47e8690da30c8f1a1230892c425_b.png" data-rawwidth="576" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="576" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/0797f47e8690da30c8f1a1230892c425_r.png">感谢 Gbike 模特 <a href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/0321af07fd2112b74fdb32dc5e8a03d1" data-hash="0321af07fd2112b74fdb32dc5e8a03d1" class="member_mention" data-editable="true" data-title="@黄玄" data-tip="p$b$0321af07fd2112b74fdb32dc5e8a03d1">@黄玄</a></p><p>▼ <b>由一台 Android 手机控制的抽象派画家</b><br><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/dcc4fd25748dd362f209ff7288752512_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/dcc4fd25748dd362f209ff7288752512_r.png"></p><p>▼ <b>Session 排队中...</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e2a5a67088e38b2862b1fd48f94f8cb2_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/e2a5a67088e38b2862b1fd48f94f8cb2_r.png">▼ <b>休息的角落</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/349ef9e558fe2e2cf63fcf4c8075ba1c_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/349ef9e558fe2e2cf63fcf4c8075ba1c_r.png">▼ <b>比上面更舒服的休息的角落</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7a7da69dcac06e7be45aab4de94fe89e_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/7a7da69dcac06e7be45aab4de94fe89e_r.png">▼ <b>Codelabs</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/5d363e823a3ccc502f4ae57f5e3e95c1_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/5d363e823a3ccc502f4ae57f5e3e95c1_r.png">▼ <b>Prepare for party</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cf8ba72d5d142ed05f78288e1f9aa2c6_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cf8ba72d5d142ed05f78288e1f9aa2c6_r.png">▼ <b>Charlie XCX</b><br><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/652e698263f5048fc590525942093be2_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/652e698263f5048fc590525942093be2_r.png"></p><p>真正的 party，I/O 大会第一天晚上的 concert。</p><p>▼ <b>Party in the U.S.A.</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/f59d4293c14e2ddcfdf86d21422c0eb6_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/f59d4293c14e2ddcfdf86d21422c0eb6_r.png">▼ <b>第二天晚上的 party</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/d0218c0a7671b2ba1e9fc117483ae412_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/d0218c0a7671b2ba1e9fc117483ae412_r.png">▼ <b>Google 员工的合唱</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/6a942e0c9631f324aa4f116481f69936_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/6a942e0c9631f324aa4f116481f69936_r.png">▼ <b>Music</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/72b83ff3a3f64335e78508fc1c717337_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/72b83ff3a3f64335e78508fc1c717337_r.png">▼ <b>Gbike racing</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7a7bda7f6d2e0d58f4676c18222fb5c9_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7a7bda7f6d2e0d58f4676c18222fb5c9_r.png">第二天晚上的 party 有一个会场是各种游戏项目，上面就是 Gbike 计时赛，在选手比赛的过程中，大屏幕上会显示 Google 街景的图片。</p><p><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.google.com/maps/streetview/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Google 街景官网<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br></p><p>▼ <b>360</b><b>° 摄影</b><br></p><p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0cb8c4822d98d1535c784ba0f8c7db22_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0cb8c4822d98d1535c784ba0f8c7db22_r.png">▼ <b>Chrome 里跑出来的小恐龙</b><br><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/1d80a1f0c0aa628003c77fe2f40d3150_b.png" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/1d80a1f0c0aa628003c77fe2f40d3150_r.png">李志的一首歌里唱到：“生活无非是痛苦和美丽”，可是 I/O 的三天，只有美丽，没有痛苦。</p>
